content:
kanyaka peŧŧāḷatbhutane
avane variṉ pariśōdhikkāṁ;
talamuṟakaḷkkādyaṉ - kīṟattuṇi cuŧŧi;
paurāṇikanāṁ vr̥ddhaneyakkanyaka prasaviccu;
malakaḷeyēntuṁ balavāne bālika lāḷiccu;
/tappaṁ dīnaṟkkēkunnōṉ
/tstanyaṁ śiśu pōl nukarunnu;
ādiyeḻāttōnāṁ sūnu
ādiyeḻāniṣṭa‌ṁ pūṇṭu;
avasānavihīnaṉ - jananattinetti.
